## Stack Summary

| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| Frontend | HTML + CSS + JS | Single-page UI |
| Frontend server | `python -m http.server` | Serves index.html on port 3000 |
| Backend framework | FastAPI + Uvicorn | REST API on port 8000 |
| NLP chunking | spaCy 3.7.4 | Sentence segmentation |
| Semantic similarity | SBERT (all-MiniLM-L6-v2) | Embedding + similarity scoring |
| LLM rewriting | Ollama (llama3.2 / mistral) | Style rewrite + flow smoothing |
| File parsing | pdfplumber + python-docx | PDF and DOCX extraction |
| Evaluation | 6 custom metrics | Human Likeness Score (HLS) |

## Pipeline Stages

| Stage | File | What it does |
|-------|------|-------------|
| 1 — Chunker | `pipeline/chunker.py` | Splits text into sentence groups using spaCy |
| 2 — Semantic Merge | `pipeline/semantic_merge.py` | Merges related chunks using SBERT embeddings |
| 3 — Style Rewriter | `pipeline/style_rewriter.py` | Rewrites each unit via Ollama LLM with tone + intensity |
| 4 — Flow Smoother | `pipeline/flow_smoother.py` | Final LLM pass to remove AI patterns and vary sentence rhythm |

## Evaluation Metrics

| Metric | File | Weight in HLS |
|--------|------|--------------|
| Burstiness | `evaluation/burstiness.py` | 20% |
| Coherence | `evaluation/coherence.py` | 30% |
| Readability | `evaluation/readability.py` | 20% |
| Connector density | `evaluation/connector_density.py` | 15% |
| Semantic similarity | `evaluation/semantic_similarity.py` | 10% |
| AI phrase score | `evaluation/ai_phrase_detector.py` | 5% |
